14 people, all level 58/61 (and ME, goddess... muahahahah)  <br>
61 pet with girdle, wepons, fireshield and valiant companion. Cannot be feared.<br>
I also resisted to fear, and got hurt sometimes for 100 Hps (rofl ! 100 HPS ? is <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>that</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> a dragon ?)<br>
